1. User Account System - Done

        Implement user signup flow.

        Capture required info as per form (name, company, email, phone, etc.).

        Store user profile in database.

        Add login & authentication (JWT or Bubble built-in auth).

2. Dashboard Message Filters - Done

        Add filters for:

        Company

        Year

        Month

        Date

        Phone number

        Email

        Add combined filter support (multiple conditions at once).

3. UI Icon Colors - Done

        WhatsApp icon green.

        Gmail icon white and red.

        SMS icon blue.

4. Dashboard Metrics -Done

        Add metrics widget showing:

        Total documents uploaded (Year/Month/Date/Today).

        Document count by company.

        Create API or workflow to fetch counts dynamically.

5. Client Count - Done

        Add a metric showing:

        Total number of clients signed up.

        New signups today/this week if needed.

6. Error Tracking - Done

        Implement error logs for:

        Failed message fetch

        Failed upload

        Failed OCR

        Add admin view to monitor errors.

        Optional: Email/SMS alert on critical failures

7. OCR Auto-Naming

        Integrate OCR (Google Vision or Tesseract).

        Extract keywords to generate filename format:

        001_documentname_date

        Auto-increment order number.

        Save final filename before uploading to Drive/database.